<subSubSection pageId="143" pageNumber="540" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="143.[161,1368,296,572]" pageId="143" pageNumber="540">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[163,522,374,407]" pageId="143" pageNumber="540">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. The Misotshi-Kabogo White-toothed Shrew would probably be listed as Data Deficient because of the absence of recent information on its distribution, habitat, and ecological requirements, for which additional studies are needed.
</paragraph>
